    1. A user can begin a game
    2. When an user begin a game then user see an introductory explanation and a button to continue to first clue
    3. When an user press the button continue to first clue the game begin and he see the first clue
    4. When the user hit the clue go to next clue
    5. When the user hit the las clue It win the game
    6. When the user win the game, a congratulation text will be show with a button of "get the gift"
    7. When the user press button get the gift, the prize won will be show with the score obtained
    8. The clue will be of 3 types: Choose the option, write the answer or be in right place
    9. When choose the option clue is show, the user must be choose between three option
    10. The options for "choose the option" will be texts or images
    11. A user that hit a clue of "choose the option" get 10x points if hit in first try, 3x if hit in second try, and x if is the third try
    12. When "write the answer" clue is show, the user must write the correct answer
    13. When "be in right place" clue is show, the user must write the geographical coordinates or be in the right place and share the device gps
    14. When a user is in a clue a countdown will be activate
    15. When a user is X time in a clue a tip help will be show for resolve the clue
    16. The tip for resolve "choose an option" will be remove a not valid option 
    17. The tip for "write the answer" that some letter will be show
    18. The tip for "be in right place" will be show the longitude

    
   Not Functional
    1. The Api must implement http and http/2
    2. The service for tips help mus be a type Push or queue protocol
    3. The system must hold on 50 concurrent user in 24/7
    4. The system must be split in microservices in Kubernetes 
    5. It should be make stress test with tool like SoapUI, Jmeter u other 
    6. The user data and game information should be persistent in a guarantee security system
